    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Can't wait to give it a try, especially because it's and idea based on project I'm currently working on where this kind of approach is suitable for.\n\nI'm suppose that something as simple as:\n\n``` Javascript\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.searchBox({\n    container: '#q',\n    debounce: 500, // in ms, 0 as default\n    minLength: 2 // 0 as default\n  })\n);\n\n```\n\nwill do the trick.\n",
